svg.title: Sketched elevation relief map showing the Moselle River slightly winding from the top left to bottom right. The towns of Toul, Épinal, and Remiremont are marked along the river. A dashed arrow goes through the map from top left to bottom right, captioned “To Rome” on the bottom right. A small perspective sketch of a road with a hill is also drawn on the bottom right, above the words Ballon d’Alsace.
